{"tid":1285423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟一齊集思廣益點樣反駁啲人嘅問題","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:54:18.000Z","uid":254923,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"901a8c84254cc6bc7d45bf430672d975bcd3e7f7","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"諗到問題嘅人一齊用我下面嗰方式提出問題跟住第一個完美反駁。等唔使俾人問到口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題：你又冇犯罪，點會驚俾人引渡返中國？<br />\n<br />\n解答：結石寶寶之家嘅發起人，趙連海，佢嘅BB唔好彩飲到啲有毒奶粉，佢諗住幫自己嘅細路爭取權益，但係最後嘅結果就係因涉嫌尋釁滋事罪入獄兩年半。我想問佢有冇罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n問題：你地一定係收咗外國錢<br />\n<br />\n解答：假設每人收咗$500<br />\n500x2000000=十億<br />\n你覺得外國勢力有冇可能用十億去令到香港癱瘓半日？<br />\n仲有我不如比多十倍$5000你，等日你沖去前面食胡椒噴霧催淚彈，好彩嘅話仲可以俾人爆頭。加多1萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n問題：警察都好慘，壓力好大...<br />\n<br />\n解答：咁老師可唔可以壓力好大打學生啊？<br />\n咁護士可唔可以壓力好大唔照顧病人啊？<br />\n咁爸爸媽媽可唔可以因為壓力好大而打自己個細路仔呀出氣啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n問題：立法會俾你地搞到咁，裝修要用5千萬啊<br />\n<br />\n解答：好平，香港一條飛機跑道未起都諗住用1000億，北京個超級國際機場都係用咗八百億左右，依家立法會5千萬簡直抵到爆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n問題：當年英國管治香港仲黑暗啦，又唔見你講？<br />\n<br />\n解答：當年你夠用Nokia啦，咁點解而家啲人用蘋果啊？追求進步呀嘛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n問題：外國如果咁樣衝入立法會人哋一早開咗槍！<br />\n<br />\n解答：人哋外國駛乜咁樣衝入立法會，佢哋每四年就可以用選票踢走唔聽人民意見嘅政府，駛乜冇咁大個險衝入立法會啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n問題：你哋二百萬人唔代表我，仲有400百萬人沉默，即係反對啦！<br />\n<br />\n解答：唔使你叫400萬人上街，你淨係吹到50萬人我都當你贏。知唔知乜嘢叫做主流民意？<br />\n<br />\n澳洲人口有二千萬，啱啱幾個月前有工會發起罷工。要求加最低工資，全國城市大概有50萬人響應罷工，議會即刻已經驚到係一個月之內提出增加最低工資議程，條啦亦都好快通過咗....大概有2百萬人受惠。所以你諗下香港個比例...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問題：你哋班後生仔冇捱過苦，我當年乜乜乜都唔係咁㗎。</span><br />\n<br />\n解答：對於你當年咁辛苦嘅經歷我表示同情，但係時代一直喺度變緊，就好似古代啲女人唔可以出街/讀書咁，唔通古代改革嘅時候又咁樣講啊？<br />\n時代唔同條件都唔同，呢個就係點解唔同年齡層之間會有咁大嘅隔膜代溝，講真啦以前同性戀係要坐監接受治療。你而家連喺條街度鬧佢地都未必敢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問題：林鄭月娥已經道歉，條例又暫緩左，你哋仲想點？</span><br />\n<br />\n解答：面對三條人，林鄭月娥1/7朝早仲喺度舉杯慶祝，晏晝有記者問佢對於呢三條人命嘅睇法，佢直頭冇回答啊！而且問咗佢咁多次佢都直接無視。<br />\n當初又話為咗一條人命嘅公義，而家死撚左四個人啦，佢做咗啲乜撚嘢？<br />\n道歉有用嘅話就唔使警察啦，同埋我哋由始至終要嘅事撤回而唔係暫緩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3015328377c5ee5dee918bda796c1d9e31fe25f8","tid":1285423,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5673db608da25cf31f226f27be9aa1e3385f4ed1","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"[size=2]問題：係外國示威者咁樣衝擊一早開咗槍<br />\n<br />\n解答：全世界警察都係+1等級機制<br />\n即係話你用拳頭嘅話，佢哋就會以體術或者短警棍。<br />\n刀概話先會攞槍。武器等級控制喺+1等級入面<br />\n<br />\n但係當日警方就使用150粒催淚彈同開咗好多槍（到而家都未正式公布開咗幾多）<br />\n但係嗰日嘅衝擊行動只係佔咗少部份示威者，大部份嘅示威者都係和平集會（就連盧偉聰同林鄭月我都承認大部份示威者係和平。）<br />\n咁點解警方要用咁多嘅武器去攻擊佢哋？合唔合理先？<br />\n屌你老味嗰日連<span style=\"color: red;\">燃燒彈都冇呀</span>，又冇放火燒車肽<br />\n同外國比真係算和平，所以你開乜撚嘢槍？<br />\n<br />\n仲有我想講警察嘅防暴裝備係好勁，佢哋嘅甲係用生果刀都界唔開，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋個盾可以擋到AK子彈</span>，頭盔更加唔使講。磚頭睇落去好似好暴力，但對全副武裝來講<span style=\"color: red;\">最多就係起到擊退作用。</span>"},{"pid":"05cba9c1705ac2c21bff661afad600b1056260ec","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd19313eccf1b2a929a8b4d8f647e9cf9551f34","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47556b426713308010575572280140b979d84942","tid":1285423,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047a7be28fce74e8f40b74fdfe5de399a1edb583","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47556b426713308010575572280140b979d84942","tid":1285423,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"分分鐘有精神病，你小心啲"},{"pid":"6cd0442c882ac624b0191e100ee2e19550f5b33c","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"6cf513a4785c1b24f0d291e5786b8356215f53c5","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"76a38ad5985921c3bffb59032dffcfb4b3c0de2f","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"ceb01761b04e25e8484c645953cda6b27bccb0d2","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"03493df7fbac947d03895491c202864516635632","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:53:50.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"43d38729cfd5297182d1afd79ea4aa243f2e4a58","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:54:01.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"b7af9f8ef9717edff927494690a5ef4ad2dbbd1b","tid":1285423,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"講得好好<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e327b21cac271f74c43350bfe32b74668007e4ed","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"6ccb7e2f3500a05572b59dab1cb48c24760e02b1","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"5237d49f1ebabe52b11f954faa8d50b81af2d395","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"2a81da298fd4e3055385fd4bcc6c9d1683472b79","tid":1285423,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:04:21.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef3b849695f20752d178417670cb281b69169f3","tid":1285423,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}